I do not like using the word "hello" or any words of the like. This includes "hi", "yo", "hey", etc.
Instead, I like going up to people and just making abnormal noises until they pay attention.

The other day, I was playing around in the pond right behind the local nuclear power plant. As I was swimming with the three eye'd fish and ten legged frogs, I realized something really crazy. Yeah, Freaky, right? I mean..I would have thought someone as sexy as me would have a cleaner room too. I guess this just goes to prove, you can't make assumptions. You'll just make an ass out of yourself and mumptions.
